main.bio: My name is Faaraan, I'm a Data Scientist. With 2.3 years of experience at Marsh McLennan and Capgemini, I bring expertise in data science and analytics. My Bachelor's in Computer Science Engineering and P.G. Diploma in Data Science equipped me with skills in Python, MySQL, Power BI, and Tableau. Proficient in predictive modeling and time series forecasting, I've developed interactive dashboards and led teams on various projects. Currently pursuing a Master's in Artificial Intelligence at Yeshiva University, I'm eager to contribute to your organization.
